{"tid":2237369,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華富凶宅鄰居：半夜敲門也不怕","createTime":"2020-10-10T08:00:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T08:25:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7bbba31d14565cb25566d577b2d209fc48c874e3","tid":2237369,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T08:00:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201010/TBU6G62U5VBNRCSKHKOU66WJFE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201010%2FTBU6G62U5VBNRCSKHKOU66WJFE%2F&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDLy9ZqCMvdeqZXcPvDNBnhI%3D&h=e23fec08\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201010%2FTBU6G62U5VBNRCSKHKOU66WJFE%2F&h=9ef21c06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201010/TBU6G62U5VBNRCSKHKOU66WJFE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n華富凶宅鄰居：半夜敲門也不怕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/QDO72Vbd4h2emPTZ1uBb-ms3f5E=/1574x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TR7P5FYGHRA73A35SHYNLFT6CM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQDO72Vbd4h2emPTZ1uBb-ms3f5E%3D%2F1574x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTR7P5FYGHRA73A35SHYNLFT6CM.jpg&h=de2daabf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■今期可供編配的公屋凶宅，黃大仙竹園南邨華園樓15樓一個單位首上榜。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】今期特快公屋編配計劃不乏凶宅，數量更是近年最多。其中在港島華富二邨華生樓9樓一個單位首次上榜，單位曾發生雙屍命案。本報記者昨日前往觀察，大廈屬舊式的天井設計，明顯有多處地方失修及殘破；即使昨日陽光普照，該處亦顯得較昏暗。現場所見曾發生命案的單位在角落位置，單位大門及鐵閘門都明顯較新淨，料房署已進行翻新，準備好再出租。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：房署逾千單位特快編配  五人枉死 凶屋王定泰樓等人揀<br />\n<br />\n與凶宅相隔數個單位的余婆婆，80年代末遷入華富邨，她記得當年的命案，男戶主「幾好」，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兒子輪候多年「住都無所謂」<br />\n<br />\n余婆婆說該單位自命案發生後「都唔多覺有人出入」，當年子女曾問她：「啲後生問我驚唔驚，我一向都唔驚呢啲」。婆婆更說：「平生不作虧心事， 半夜敲門也不怕。我呢啲係唔驚，一切由天吩咐。」她的兒子已輪候公屋多年，正在同區租住私樓，月租約一萬元，正輪候公屋，並曾申請特快公屋計劃，「我哋家人唔驚呢啲嘢，打個比喻，就算（住）嗰間都無所謂」。<br />\n<br />\n黃大仙竹園南邨華園樓15樓一個單位亦都是新上榜，。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"6fd8ae09216490fa1916070247df745576bfc358","tid":2237369,"uid":140726,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T08:08:43.000Z","msg":"最恐怖嘅係窮鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"981de8fbd3bb557d847970103f72bc354f28840a","tid":2237369,"uid":197782,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T08:15:31.000Z","msg":"香港人仲恐怖過鬼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c5ee26541805078a617340de36881957d55dec0","tid":2237369,"uid":73565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7bbba31d14565cb25566d577b2d209fc48c874e3","tid":2237369,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T08:00:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201010/TBU6G62U5VBNRCSKHKOU66WJFE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201010%2FTBU6G62U5VBNRCSKHKOU66WJFE%2F&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDLy9ZqCMvdeqZXcPvDNBnhI%3D&h=e23fec08\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201010%2FTBU6G62U5VBNRCSKHKOU66WJFE%2F&h=9ef21c06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201010/TBU6G62U5VBNRCSKHKOU66WJFE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n華富凶宅鄰居：半夜敲門也不怕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/QDO72Vbd4h2emPTZ1uBb-ms3f5E=/1574x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TR7P5FYGHRA73A35SHYNLFT6CM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQDO72Vbd4h2emPTZ1uBb-ms3f5E%3D%2F1574x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTR7P5FYGHRA73A35SHYNLFT6CM.jpg&h=de2daabf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■今期可供編配的公屋凶宅，黃大仙竹園南邨華園樓15樓一個單位首上榜。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】今期特快公屋編配計劃不乏凶宅，數量更是近年最多。其中在港島華富二邨華生樓9樓一個單位首次上榜，單位曾發生雙屍命案。本報記者昨日前往觀察，大廈屬舊式的天井設計，明顯有多處地方